text:
当我们检验一款新的疫苗是否有效时，通常会使用疫苗有效性\(\pi\)(Vaccine Efficacy)这个指标。让\(P_1\), \(P_2\)分别为安慰剂组和接种疫苗组的发病率；\(N_1\), \(N_2\)分别为安慰剂组和接种疫苗组的群体总数；\(X, Y\)分别为安慰剂和疫苗组的病例人数。则\(X \overset{..d}{\sim}\text{Binomial}(N_1, P_1)\), \(Y \overset{..d}{\sim}\text{Binomial}(N_2, P_2)\)。疫苗有效性为：
\[
  \pi = 1-(P_2/P_1)
  \tag{2.1}
\]
原假设和备择假设为：\[
  H_0: \pi \leq \pi_0 \text{ versus } \ H_1:\pi>\pi_0   
  \tag{2.2}
\]如果一个疾病发病率较低，我们就需要更多受试者参加实验，在这种情况下\(X, Y\)可以被近似成为独立的泊松分布，
也就是\(X \overset{..d}{\sim}\text{Poisson}(\lambda_1)\), \(Y \overset{..d}{\sim}\text{Poisson}(\lambda_2)\) \(\lambda_1 = N_1\cdot P_1, \lambda_2 = N_2\cdot P_2\).\(Y\)给定\(T\)的条件概率分布为
\[
  Y|T \sim \text{Binomial}(T, \theta)=\binom{T}{k} \theta^k(1-\theta)^{T-k} \text{} T = X + Y, \theta = \frac{\lambda_1}{\lambda_1=\lambda_2}
  \tag{2.3}
\]
此时原假设和备择假设为：\[
  H_0: \theta \geq \theta_0 \text{ versus } \ H_1:\theta<\theta_0 \text{ } \theta_0 = \frac{1-\pi_0}{2-\pi_0}
  \tag{2.4}
\]计算的P value 公式为
\[
p = \Pr[Y \leq Y_{\text{obs}} \mid Y \sim \text{Binomial}(T, \theta_0)] = \sum_{k=0}^{Y_{\text{obs}}} \binom{T}{k} \theta_0^k (1 - \theta_0)^{T - k}
\tag{2.5}
\]计算的P value 公式为
\[
p = \Pr[Y \leq Y_{\text{obs}} \mid Y \sim \text{Binomial}(T, \theta_0)] = \sum_{k=0}^{Y_{\text{obs}}} \binom{T}{k} \theta_0^k (1 - \theta_0)^{T - k}
\tag{2.5}
\]计算Statistical power公式为
\[
1 - \beta = \Pr[Y \leq Y_c \mid Y \sim \text{Binomial}(T, \theta_1)] = \sum_{k=0}^{Y_c} \binom{T}{k} \theta_1^k (1 - \theta_1)^{T - k}
\tag{2.6}
\]计算Statistical power公式为
\[
1 - \beta = \Pr[Y \leq Y_c \mid Y \sim \text{Binomial}(T, \theta_1)] = \sum_{k=0}^{Y_c} \binom{T}{k} \theta_1^k (1 - \theta_1)^{T - k}
\tag{2.6}
\]计算临床实验所需样本量公式为
\[
N_2 = T/[(2-\pi_1)/P_1]
\tag{2.7}
\]计算临床实验所需样本量公式为
\[
N_2 = T/[(2-\pi_1)/P_1]
\tag{2.7}
\]计算样本量所需的变量为\(\pi_0, \pi_1, \alpha\), 期望统计功效(1-\(\beta\))和安慰剂组发病率(\(P_1\))。详细推导过程可以看 Ivan S. F. Chan Norman R. Bohidar1 和 Matthew M Loiacono2

